column5: Beautifully decorated, 3 bd / 2 bath, clean, modern house. 2 miles from Town Center, residential, fenced-in, quiet area. Nearly 2,000 sq. feet. 2 car garage. One-level. Refrigerator, washer, dryer, tv (Roku, including Sling, and digital local channels), plus high-speed internet.  Professional property manager on call.
column8: 3BR/2 Full Bath Entire House, The Woodlands
